## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in sources that may favor particular religious or secular viewpoints. Additionally, the complexity of religious influence varies significantly across different cultural and political contexts, which may not be fully captured in this analysis. Further research could explore the evolving role of religion in increasingly secular societies and its impact on emerging policy issues.